 in this paper) than several usual\ntracers. Estimating the Galactic dust extinction on the basis of this emission\nallows us to find a smaller dispersion in the NUV-i colour of background\ngalaxies at a given E(B-V)than with other tracers. The diffuse light mosaics\nobtained in this work are made publicly available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2015 09:49:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
